title: Birte Glang
summary: Birte Glang (born 15 April 1980) is a German actress, brand ambassador, and fashion model. She started her career as a series regular on the award winning TV soap opera Unter uns. In 2012, she starred in the German James Bond parody Agent Ranjid rettet die Welt. In 2014, she was booked for a film with the comedian Nick Offerman.
